https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0 for the full text.

This subproject does not modify the AOSP source files in place. Behavioural
differences from upstream are achieved entirely through:

  - the porting/ shim headers redirecting Android-only system includes to
    glibc-compatible substitutes;
  - the -DGST_C2_LINUX_PORT define gating Android-specific code paths inside
    the vendored sources where they cannot be hidden by an include override.

The original Apache-2.0 NOTICE / LICENSE headers at the top of each vendored
file are preserved verbatim.
